ffmpeg is a command line multimedia convertor

to install the ffmpeg you can follow the instructions in the following article:
https://linuxize.com/post/how-to-install-ffmpeg-on-ubuntu-18-04/


for exmaple this command can convert a .mp3 to .ogg file:
'''
ffmpeg -i input.mp3 output.ogg
'''

you can find more tutorials with a simple google search.
